me":"2021-02-19T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"一年前成班醫護罷工叫政府封關，不過柒婆死都唔肯封，搞到武肺傳左入黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年之後當日罷工既醫護比人清算，工會主席比人用國安法拉鳩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢地唔單止無縮過，到今日仲企出黎，叫大家<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>唔好下載安心出行</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T4EFopg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT4EFopg.png&h=4d18593f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住就比成個政府狙擊，個facebook比成班五毛湧入去洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107732697364538/posts/271025477701925/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107732697364538%2Fposts%2F271025477701925%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=2a2f23bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107732697364538/posts/271025477701925/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n其實到而家仲堅持出聲仲要擺街站既團體都無幾多個，遲早呢班醫護分分鐘比政府拉埋炒埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好當醫護係condom，比佢地見到香港人支持你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw入去page睇先知佢地之前仲拍左段宣傳片，雖然有啲似火炭麗琪但係都幾撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全係預示緊香港既將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過唔係好見有人share，大家都可以幫手share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/3LEYiNajHx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F3LEYiNajHx%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=83406510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/3LEYiNajHx/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74522e348087ea3440bbe2ae21db0d5987b74193","tid":2414811,"uid":342828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:25:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"403cbdf3fa27b44b6262e6126c01e07b640a5cc6","tid":2414811,"uid":40381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"推下先。認真post 冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da253761f53fa29b74a8ca72fff574ca05b6d6a","tid":2414811,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665781ab66c3676ead67d4647ef9022f3e2c7b9d","tid":2414811,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c00910965f43a1de034db1ca67c60e04419e0e0","tid":2414811,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8650dce3b3125f7b4a9b625a3e9203bdc295347d","tid":2414811,"uid":275384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927703a7ddbe606e27c8143d6f481d3480d29115","tid":2414811,"uid":266701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/l